tool_description: Get access to different tiers of the most expensive API. Not everyone can access one or all tiers as this API is so very expensive. Those who posses access to this API are in a very limited circle of persons/companies.
title: Most Expensive API

api_list.name: /basic
api_list.description: Basic tier of the most expensive API.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://most-expensive-api.p.rapidapi.com/basic"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "most-expensive-api.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
